  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-4）：字节跳动推出 Ouro 循环语言模型，预训练阶段直接构建推理能力，革新大模型知识操纵范式",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500153&idx=1&sn=f1d0941dd78c097cfc1a9a38e4e1eb73",
  "date": "2025-11-04 10:06:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2025-11-04 18:06</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p>循环语言模型Ouro，“端到端语言模型” 开发的项目集合AutoDeco，多模态数据集PhysToolBench，多通道“渲染机”MagicNodes，开源工具Promptify，自动化交易平台AI-Trader</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c5c1c2d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7phx60p3SnBrDJwINkBE1vrbh1Bv5zYk8M7hibKJPicXL8LpyiaZOicvsdQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Ouro</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"500\" data-imgfileid=\"100016492\" data-ratio=\"0.43148148148148147\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b6706920&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU72WzPuicGfr9tSC04CbSUPyjX4kEnbrWs6M2ZaAbgibFvwxkTxenP1byg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Ouro 是字节跳动 Seed 团队联合多家机构推出的循环语言模型（Looped Language Models）项目，旨在将推理能力直接构建到预训练阶段，而非依赖训练后的 “思维链” 等显式文本生成过程。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目包含 Ouro-1.4B、Ouro-1.4B-Thinking、Ouro-2.6B、Ouro-2.6B-Thinking 等多类预训练模型，核心采用共享权重层堆栈的循环架构，集成学习到的 “退出门” 实现自适应计算 —— 简单输入可提前退出以节省资源，复杂输入则分配更多迭代次数进行深层处理，在潜在空间构建 “潜在思想链” 以提升知识操纵能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ouro2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ouro2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：AutoDeco</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1168\" data-height=\"648\" data-imgfileid=\"100016490\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b55c5f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7QucmbvmlZXgvGjzVeLHlEPTGswn51aGIK0SqqeFOMTBuDabsC2QSSA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AutoDeco 是一个聚焦于 “端到端语言模型” 开发的项目集合，旨在终结传统语言模型依赖的手动解码流程，实现从输入到输出的全链路自动化处理。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目基于多种主流基础模型（如 Llama-Nemotron、Qwen3、GPT-OSS 等），通过集成 AutoDeco 专用头部模块，构建出真正意义上的端到端大语言模型，涵盖 7B 到 235B 不同参数规模的模型版本（如 AutoDeco-R1-Distill-Qwen-7B、AutoDeco-Qwen3-235B-A22B-Thinking-2507 等），满足不同场景下的性能与效率需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autodeco-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autodeco-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：PhysToolBench</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"746\" data-imgfileid=\"100016489\" data-ratio=\"0.6453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1156\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d13af5e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7yeslJ8uV49zCtUpaAHrjNueLibGrIp152rLHfw6sfVQEia9Kya02beww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★PhysToolBench 是一个专注于物理工具选择的多模态数据集，旨在通过图像和文本的结合来解决实际任务中的工具选择问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该数据集包含了多种日常任务场景，用户需要根据提供的图像和文本描述选择合适的工具。PhysToolBench 适用于图像-文本到文本的任务，支持机器学习模型的训练和评估，帮助提升模型在实际应用中的决策能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/phystoolbench\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/phystoolbench</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：MagicNodes</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016495\" data-ratio=\"0.5018518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d866bcd1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7DFZILAFxuP5ia5vVgd3zNXwIVtfNmmHTN6uBaLATb7uV1pABfO4icX2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MagicNodes 是一个即插即用的多通道“渲染机”，专为SD/SDXL模型设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过简单的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">单节点启动</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，用户可以获得专家级的渲染结果。其核心技术包括</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">ZeResFDG（频率解耦+重缩放+零投影）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">始终开启的QSilk微粒稳定器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，辅以实用的稳定器（如NAG、局部掩码、EPS、Muse Blend、Polish）。该项目提供四通道预设，确保输出结果稳健、干净且细节丰富。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/magicnodes2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/magicnodes2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Promptify</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"478\" data-imgfileid=\"100016487\" data-ratio=\"0.41203703703703703\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1160\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d85f4072&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7pzdp1BBFERbmDDPzNntL2GYZDN1iaTnZ9WdomgDhVHzxg8k1cWN0vlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Promptify是一个用于Prompt工程的开源工具，旨在通过使用GPT等生成模型解决自然语言处理（NLP）问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目支持多种NLP任务，如命名实体识别（NER）、多标签分类、问答生成等。用户可以通过简单的API调用，快速生成适用于不同任务的Prompt，并进行模型推理。Promptify还支持自定义示例和样本的添加，输出结果以Python对象形式呈现，便于解析和过滤。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/promptify\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/promptify</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🤖 Agent 开发</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：AI-Trader</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"842\" data-imgfileid=\"100016486\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02693718&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky1Vl1WKE8icYtcPFfibsbCU7LKxc2OOQh5cLu8oUtI3R4VYOhkYGaG95B32KRLJ4P2L2ZCHBFLH6rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★AI-Trader 是一个自动化交易平台，允许多个人工智能模型在 NASDAQ 100 和 SSE 50 市场中进行自主竞争，以确定哪个模型能够产生最高的利润。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目完全依赖 AI 进行独立分析、决策和执行，无需人工干预。通过 MCP 工具链，AI 可以通过标准化工具调用完成所有交易操作。平台支持多模型竞争、实时性能分析和市场情报集成，提供全面的交易记录、仓位监控和盈亏分析。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI